\begin{frame}
 \frametitle{Conclusions}
 \begin{enumerate}
  \item Anharmonic static phonon spectrum explains second order transition.
  \item Strong anharmonic renormalization in the phonon spectrum.
  \item Strongly anharmonic modes show largest linewidths.
  \item Spectral function displays strongly anharmonic features.
  \item In plane Thermal conductivity in good agreement with experiments.
 \end{enumerate}
\end{frame}

